headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires First Capital Financial Services
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of New Zealand-based First Capital Financial Services (First Capital) and its affiliate First Capital Wealth Management. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
